      "writtenOn": "2019-12-06T00:19:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s a slight change in behavior for two pass decoding. Previously, *rowsDecoded could be unchanged for e.g. a SkCodec::kIncompleteInput result on a dependent frame.\n\nI\u0027m still not 100% confident I understand what the rowsDecoded parameter does, so I\u0027m not sure if this behavior change would break something subtle. If you\u0027re OK with it, though, then Done.",
      "parentUuid": "36b01eec_89f9dd60",
